premise_source_doc_sentence: Ganda Hendathi  (  English : husband and wife  )  is a 2006 Indian Kannada erotic thriller film , directed by Ravi Shrivatsa and produced by Shailendra Babu .
This film stars newcomers Vishal Hegde , Sanjjanaa and Thilak Shekar in lead roles .
The film is a remake of Hindi hit film Murder  (  2004  )  , starring Mallika Sherawat , Emraan Hashmi and Ashmit Patel .
The film created huge controversies upon release for its excessive erotic scenes and content .
The score and soundtrack was composed by Gurukiran for the lyrics of V. Manohar and Hrudaya Shiva .

Ganda Hendathi  (  English : husband and wife  )  is a 2006 Indian Kannada erotic thriller film , directed by Ravi Shrivatsa and produced by Shailendra Babu .
